# Unit (Jest)
- Services & Utils testen.  
- Firestore via Emulator mocken.
- Zod-Schemas: Validierung testen.
- Custom Hooks: useAuth, useGeoLocation, useResponsive.
- Date-Utilities: Deutsche Lokalisierung testen.  

# Integration
- React Testing Library für Pages & Forms.
- Error Boundaries: Fehlerbehandlung testen.
- React Query: Cache-Verhalten testen.
- Form-Validierung: Zod + react-hook-form Integration.  

# E2E
- Playwright.  
- Kritischer Flow: Auftrag → Worktime → Signatur → Export.  
- Standard Viewport: 1440x900 (Desktop-First).
- DSGVO-Compliance: Arbeitszeit-Grenzen testen.
- Responsive Testing: Desktop, Tablet, Mobile.
